Kuzari Group LLC


                  Kuzari Group LLC operates as a private investment and strategic development firm. It focuses on investing in and developing small businesses which represents long-term value creation opportunities. The company was founded by Benjamin Gerut in 2009 and is headquartered in New York, NY.                





